{"tid":205738,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[超短篇/搞事]有一日，阿丁佢許了一個願","createTime":"2017-04-18T04:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T11:16:32.000Z","uid":55505,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"539d3e61b7788cb45b6073ff463d9fef7d2fd725","tid":205738,"uid":55505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T04:09:12.000Z","msg":"阿丁跟阿欣是一對熱戀中的情侶<br />\n<br />\n兩人都不算富有，但也很幸福開心<br />\n<br />\n有一日，阿欣跟阿丁說「希望我地之後都咁幸福」<br />\n<br />\n阿丁在阿欣面前向天許願道「只要妳幸福，我做乜都冇所謂」<br />\n<br />\n天神聽到了<br />\n<br />\n過了幾日阿欣跟阿丁分手了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿欣最後與有錢的前男友復合然後過著幸福快樂的日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「雖然說想給你幸福的人是我，但沒有能力令你幸福，也是沒用；儘管希望令你幸福的人是我，也只是說說而已」"},{"pid":"2defde00c8c4a0ceb36987ffb66ae07410b1ec77","tid":205738,"uid":55505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:50:23.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n自己覆自己算了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5410e74637c65184eeb51efd4bd265151a2c7b2e","tid":205738,"uid":79427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T11:16:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n自己覆自己算了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想人點覆"}]}